name: r-cobs
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "1.3-5" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-cobs
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/cobs_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/cobs/cobs_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 7fae7da8f940975d544120c836e2d3b874f9b0cbab9631851ce986709f51c611

build:
  merge_build_host: true  # [win]
  number: 0
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}              # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_c') }}        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}filesystem        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}make
    - {{ posix }}sed               # [win]
    - {{ posix }}coreutils         # [win]
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-sparsem >=1.6
    - r-quantreg >=4.65
  run:
    - r-base
    - {{ native }}gcc-libs         # [win]
    - r-sparsem >=1.6
    - r-quantreg >=4.65

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('cobs')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('cobs')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: http://curves-etc.r-forge.r-project.org/ http://r-forge.r-project.org/R/?group_id=846
  license: GPL-2.0-or-later
  summary: Qualitatively Constrained (Regression) Smoothing Splines via Linear Programming and Sparse Matrices.
  license_family: GPL2
  license_file:
    - {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
